(62, '6th Regular Session', '2025-02-10', 0x75706c6f6164732f36746820526567756c61722053657373696f6e2e706466, '7.6', 'Resolution No. 050-2025 of the Sangguniang Panlalawigan Acting on Resolutions and Ordinances submitted by the different Sangguniang Bayan, this province\r\nTALISAY:\r\n1. Resolution No. 174-2024 Reclassifying the Land Use of the Property declared thru Deed of Grant of Home Lot Rights in the name of Linda Defeo Rodriguez,located at Barangay Sta Elena, Talisay under ARP No. GR 2014-HH-11-014-0068 with PIN NO. 025-11-014-02-029 with a total area of 200 sq m portion of 3,000 has from Agricultural to Commercial Use- - - Referred to PPDO\r\n2. Resolution No. 185-2024  Adopting the 4th  Subsidiary  AIP CY 2024 of the Municipality of Talisay of Talisay, Camarines Norte as approved by MDC of the same municipality amounting to Php4,590,000.00- - - Referred to PPDO\r\n3. Resolution No. 186-2024 Adopting MDC Resolution No. 013,s,2024 Approving the Change of Project Title of 20% Development Fund CY 2024 Project, from Construction of Evacuation Center (Phase 1) to Concreting of P-1, Barangay Road of Barangay Cahabaan - - - Referred to PPDO\r\n4. Resolution No. 200-2024 Adopting the 5th Subsidiary Annual Investment Program CY 2024 of the Municipality of Talisay as approved by the MDC amounting to Php1,500,000.00)- - - Referred to PPDO', '', 'For the Information of the Honorable Sangguniang Bayan', '', NULL, ''),
