(64, '6th Regular Session', '2025-02-10', 0x75706c6f6164732f36746820526567756c61722053657373696f6e2e706466, '7.8', 'Resolutions/Ordinance submitted by the Sangguniang Barangay of Cahabaan, this municipality\r\n1. Resolution No. 01,s.2025/Barangay Ordinance No. 01,s.2025 Creating the Position of Barangay Driver of Barangay Cahabaan, Talisay, Camarines Norte in accordance with Art. 25 of the Implementing Rules and Regulations of RA 7160, otherwise known as the Local Government Code of 1991.\r\n2. Resolution No. 03,s.2025 Concurring the Appointment of Mr. Jerry C. Mase to the position of Barangay Environmental Police of Cahabaan\r\n3. Resolution No. 04,s.2025 Concurring the Appointment of Ms Aiza Manggayo Yasis to the Position of Barangay Record Keeper of Barangay Cahabaan\r\n4. Resolution No. 05,s.2025 Concurring the Appointment of Mr. Alexander E. Cantos, Sr. to the Position of Barangay Driver of Barangay Cahabaan.', '', 'approved (February 24, 2025)', '', NULL, '');
